# This is a "git flake": nix copies only the git-tracked files into the store on
# `nix develop`, instead of the entire ~60G working tree (build/, swift/,
# llvm-project/, …). Track only the recipe (flake + build script + docs); ignore
# everything else (the Swift source checkouts and build/ are fetched/produced
# locally, not part of this repo).
/*
!/.gitignore
!/flake.nix
!/flake.lock
!/dobuild.sh
!/README.md
!/HACKING.md
